*Bogat* čovek ima puno novca. (The wealthy man has a lot of money.)

Ona je *bogata* devojka. (She is a wealthy girl.)

*Bogatstvo* je stvaranje dobrih stvari. (Wealth is the creation of good things.)

Ne želim biti *bogat*, već srećan. (I don't want to be wealthy, but happy.)

On je *bogatstvom* obasipao svoje voljene. (He showered his beloved ones with wealth.)